pe" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !impor=
tant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom=
-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  it did</a>. One way for UBS to sa=
ve on headcount is by no longer having to compete with Credit Suisse for de=
als. Another way for UBS to save on headcount is by no longer doing whole c=
ategories of deals that Credit Suisse did (the ones that blew up Credit Sui=
sse). The less competition there is among big banks, the less any bank will=
 feel the need to take dumb risks to win business.</p>
