<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The bankruptcy declaration says:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The purpose of these Chapter 11 Ca=
ses is for the Company to maximize value by conducting a robust sale proces=
s, reducing its cash burn to preserve resources, and centralizing the claim=
s asserted against the Company to efficiently resolve those claims and prov=
ide meaningful recoveries to its creditors and, if sufficient, its sharehol=
ders.=C2=A0</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">As in any bankruptcy, one goal is to maximize =
the value of assets, by selling the company for as much as it can get and b=
y suing Foxconn for damages. And as in any bankruptcy, the other goal is to=
