<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here is a fun art project:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">I go around on social media saying th=
at I have a clever hedge fund that makes returns of 420% per year by tradin=
g at nighttime in a multibillion-dollar secret market run by foreign centra=
l banks and the Illuminati.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-4"=
