nt; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[4]</span>
</a>
</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">I tell people that if they send m=
e their money I can get those 420% returns for them.</li>=09<li style=3D"ma=
rgin-bottom: 5px;">You send me your money.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-botto=
m: 5px;">I keep it.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You complain.<=
/li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">I say =E2=80=9Cno no no, this was =
an art project, I am pointing out the contradictions in global capitalism b=
y showing the wild stuff that people believe.=E2=80=9D</li>=09<li style=3D"=
margin-bottom: 5px;">You say =E2=80=9Cwell, fine, but give me my money back=
.=E2=80=9D</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">I say =E2=80=9Cno keepi=
ng your money is what makes it art.=E2=80=9D</li>
</ol>
